  </sponsors>
  <source>Cyclacel Pharmaceuticals, Inc.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study to find the highest tolerable dose of sapacitabine that can be given
      to patients with advanced leukemias or myelodysplastic syndromes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
